Zapdos (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0144: Articuno
Pokémon
#0146: Moltres →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Zapdos (TCG Pocket).

Zapdos has been featured on 33 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Zapdos cards are normally Lightning-type, Colorless-type, or Fighting-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Zapdos

Zapdos
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
